Privacy Policy for
Hyperion Games (UK)
Last modified: 13 September 2023
Our Privacy Policy explains:
What information we collect and why we collect it.
How we use that information.
The information stored on your device.
We’ve tried to keep it as simple as possible. Your privacy matters to us, if you have any questions
contact us
(mail) or
contact us
(form)
Information that we collect
As of 2019 we no longer collect any device information.
We collect no data, as our applications are predominantly for children.
Your child’s name and progress stay in your device and any backups you make (including iCloud).
How we use information that we collect
As we no longer collect any information – we do not use it.
Local Stored Information
Your progress, score, achievements and name are stored as part of the application and any backups you make.
